{"tid":1018952,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［絲請入］韓式剪髮冇得輸 點解香港Salon咁垃圾","createTime":"2019-02-12T14:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T13:37:00.000Z","uid":65382,"like":17,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"571cb7fd06dd642cd2a9c3034f068004bb9fb87f","tid":1018952,"uid":65382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"作為一個天生攣毛爆炸髮質嘅我以為我呢一世只能靠垃圾mk負離子直髮過世。<br />\n但我發現原來韓國流行一種「魔法電髮」嘅技術，係可以令頭髮貼服之餘，亦不失自然同空氣感。<br />\n對於垃圾髮質嘅我嚟講，簡直係猶如整容嘅存在一樣，可以令頭髮投胎。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JyQODJ4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJyQODJ4.png&h=b9c86f4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n拉直髮根同時又卷起頭髮<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GrU4b4d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrU4b4d.png&h=18fad668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後落藥水固定造型<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aJqu7C6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaJqu7C6.png&h=a02bea47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n卷完放返頭髮出嚟好似啊豬媽咁，但唔洗驚，洗完頭吹返乾就冇事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cgpckYH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcgpckYH.png&h=4bed6a0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xgC5FYN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxgC5FYN.png&h=ed171ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港髮型屋真係追九條街都追唔到人哋技術，唔怪之得「韓式剪髮」可以成為一個派別，流行嘅指標<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N4x5FZH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN4x5FZH.png&h=901aec0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人哋剪劉海亦都非常自然，頭髮厚度適中，貼近面頰可以剪出自然弧度。<br />\n但唔知點解，香港髮型師係剪唔出呢種劉海，一係就剪到直角咁，一係就見到好齊好齊，剪唔出韓國劉海嗰種自然，唔知有冇絲打明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdda7540a335202dfeeb483c9c7eed70253f6551","tid":1018952,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"韓你老母"},{"pid":"1776036a74aa644c3ffe8aba42c6a4b952840d59","tid":1018952,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:59:44.000Z","msg":"睇到好想去韓國剪髮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eef81ae9e7535efc60653fe8d4efbb78f9d901a","tid":1018952,"uid":65382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fdda7540a335202dfeeb483c9c7eed70253f6551","tid":1018952,"uid":2419,"like":8,"dislike":4,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T14:57:39.000Z","msg":"韓你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁泡菜囉"},{"pid":"0a26ac680332e91f3b0d95ad7b70e9b9be89856c","tid":1018952,"uid":44277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"大把香港嘅日本髮型屋做到呢啲效果。。"},{"pid":"53f76f77abfd13dce3b0d0c2b5159b06f421991c","tid":1018952,"uid":80814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:07:30.000Z","msg":"喺香港可以去做Paimore"},{"pid":"e458a03da7ede33a4ab66a34632da090a177ef62","tid":1018952,"uid":35420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:08:02.000Z","msg":"好核突<br />\n日式最靚"},{"pid":"b069275221c886f15abc848008bce0469a534f06","tid":1018952,"uid":127571,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"唔關技術時，香港既天氣，整咩髮都係柒"},{"pid":"4a69d1b601043df3bce731b5c38bb3836cee6948","tid":1018952,"uid":82482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T15:10:31.000Z","msg":"整完影個頭嚟睇下"},{"pid":"c2bd02cbadf27251a9f350288ef10ecb68fb5af9","tid":1018952,"uid":173530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-13T13:36:32.000Z","msg":"好想整睇唔明韓文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1082ce026b4b4c0119fd4e8daa3b1031d86c61","tid":1018952,"uid":126947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a26ac680332e91